  },
  {
   "offset": 11,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "a carefree fellow in a ludicrous costume.",
   "zh": "一個身著荒誕戲服、無憂無慮的傢伙。",
   "zh_bytes": 34,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 55,
   "len": 68,
   "en": "\"Ho eyo he hum, I've got a @clue! It's important, and just for you!\"",
   "zh": "「叮叮咚咚噹啷噹，俺有@clue（線索）特意俏！事關重大莫等閒，專為汝來報！」",
   "zh_bytes": 65,
   "note": "招牌順口溜 [r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 126,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "name",
   "zh": "name",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword 觸發詞"
  },
  {
   "offset": 131,
   "len": 91,
   "en": "\"Why, I'm Chuckles the @jester, of course! You've @heard of me haven't you? Sure you have!\"",
   "zh": "「哎呀，俺正是@jester（弄臣）笑笑！汝@heard（聽說）過俺吧？想必聽過囉！」",
   "zh_bytes": 54,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 234,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "hear",
   "zh": "hear",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 239,
   "len": 42,
   "en": "\"You've heard a word? Why that's @absurd!\"",
   "zh": "「聞風一句話？簡直@absurd（荒誕）無涯！」",
   "zh_bytes": 31,
   "note": "押韻"
  },
  {
   "offset": 282,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "job",
   "zh": "job",
   "zh_bytes": 3,
   "note": "len=3 keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 286,
   "len": 76,
   "en": "\"To @jape, to jeer, to prance, to frolic! To keep this place unmelancholic!\"",
   "zh": "「@jape（戲謔）嘲諷蹦跳鬧！叫此地永不寂寥！」",
   "zh_bytes": 37,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 365,
   "len": 81,
   "en": "\"I practice @tomfoolery for Lord @British - or anyone else who passes too close.\"",
   "zh": "「俺為@tomfoolery（愚行）顛王獻上@British（愚行）——湊近的人也跟著遭殃。」",
   "zh_bytes": 50,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 452,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "jape",
   "zh": "jape",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 457,
   "len": 12,
   "en": "\"And @jeer!\"",
   "zh": "「再@jeer（諷）！」",
   "zh_bytes": 11,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 475,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "jeer",
   "zh": "jeer",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 480,
   "len": 43,
   "en": "\"And @prance! To dance a Corybantic dance!\"",
   "zh": "「再@prance（蹦跳）！跳支瘋癲狂歌舞飄！」",
   "zh_bytes": 31,
   "note": "Corybantic→瘋癲狂躁 [r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 529,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "pran,danc",
   "zh": "pran,danc",
   "zh_bytes": 9,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 539,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"Jeer and prance! Prance and @frolic!\"",
   "zh": "「譏笑又蹦跳！蹦跳又@frolic（嬉鬧）！」",
   "zh_bytes": 29,
   "note": "[r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 583,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "frol",
   "zh": "frol",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 588,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"I lurch 'round like an @alcoholic!\"",
   "zh": "「俺搖晃如@alcoholic（醉漢）顛倒！」",
   "zh_bytes": 23,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 630,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "tom",
   "zh": "tom",
   "zh_bytes": 3,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 634,
   "len": 44,
   "en": "\"'Cause Dick and Harry both called in sick.\"",
   "zh": "「因為張三李四都告病請假了。」",
   "zh_bytes": 30,
   "note": "Tom,Dick,Harry 英諺 [r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 684,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "lord,brit",
   "zh": "lord,brit",
   "zh_bytes": 9,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 694,
   "len": 53,
   "en": "\"Call him Mr. @Nose... But don't tell him I said so!\"",
   "zh": "「叫他@Nose（大鼻）生……可別讓他聽見俺說的！」",
   "zh_bytes": 39,
   "note": "[r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 753,
   "len": 7,
   "en": "mr,nose",
   "zh": "mr,nose",
   "zh_bytes": 7,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 761,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"Shhh! Don't let him know I told you!\"",
   "zh": "「噓！可別讓他曉得俺說了！」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 800,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "clue",
   "zh": "clue",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
