   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 816,
   "len": 76,
   "en": "\"If hints were mints and mints were hints, think what a @world it would be!\"",
   "zh": "「若提示是糖球，糖球是提示，這@world（世界）豈不妙！」",
   "zh_bytes": 45,
   "note": "[r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 898,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "ques,ches",
   "zh": "ques,ches",
   "zh_bytes": 9,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 908,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"A quest, a chest, oh what a @jest!\"",
   "zh": "「@jest（試煉）、寶箱，何等笑談一場！」",
   "zh_bytes": 32,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 950,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "jest",
   "zh": "jest",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 961,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "teac,prea",
   "zh": "teac,prea",
   "zh_bytes": 9,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 971,
   "len": 45,
   "en": "\"To teach, to preach, what waste of @speech!\"",
   "zh": "「又教又道，盡費@speech（唇舌）囉！」",
   "zh_bytes": 27,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1022,
   "len": 39,
   "en": "mint,worl,spee,lurc,alco,word,absu,done",
   "zh": "mint,worl,spee,lurc,alco,word,absu,done",
   "zh_bytes": 39,
   "note": "keyword 短碼列保留英文"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1062,
   "len": 20,
   "en": "\"I just said @that!\"",
   "zh": "「俺剛@that就這麼說！」",
   "zh_bytes": 19,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1088,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "that",
   "zh": "that",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1093,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"You just said '@that!'\"",
   "zh": "你剛說了『@that就這麼』！",
   "zh_bytes": 21,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1123,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "nyst",
   "zh": "nyst",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1128,
   "len": 19,
   "en": "\"Oh, he's no @fun.\"",
   "zh": "「噢，他無@fun（樂趣）！」",
   "zh_bytes": 19,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1153,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "fun",
   "zh": "fun",
   "zh_bytes": 3,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1157,
   "len": 37,
   "en": "\"I'll show you fun before I'm @done!\"",
   "zh": "「俺玩給汝看，玩到@done（玩完）！」",
   "zh_bytes": 27,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1200,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "bye",
   "zh": "bye",
   "zh_bytes": 3,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1212,
   "len": 66,
   "en": "\"Ho ho, hee hee, thou art funnier than me! To ask a jester of $Z!\"",
   "zh": "「呵呵嘻嘻，汝比俺更滑稽！竟問弄臣何為$Z！」",
   "zh_bytes": 44,
   "note": "$Z=時辰變數保留"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1284,
   "len": 68,
   "en": "\"Yes, it's crucial to your @quest. Do you want to know what it is?\" ",
   "zh": "「沒錯，這對汝的@quest（試煉）至關緊要。汝可想知道是啥麼？」",
   "zh_bytes": 51,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1353,
   "len": 2,
   "en": "yn",
   "zh": "yn",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "y/n prompt"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1358,
   "len": 35,
   "en": "\"Perhaps I don't want to tell you!\"",
   "zh": "「或許俺不想告訴你哪！」",
   "zh_bytes": 24,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1396,
   "len": 31,
   "en": "\"Perhaps I'll tell you anyway!\"",
   "zh": "「或許俺還是會告訴你！」",
   "zh_bytes": 24,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1430,
   "len": 23,
   "en": "\"Do you think I will?\" ",
   "zh": "「你覺得俺會說嗎？」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1454,
   "len": 2,
   "en": "yn",
   "zh": "yn",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "y/n prompt"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1459,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"How foolish of you to think so! ",
   "zh": "「汝這麼想真是傻氣！",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1495,
   "len": 40,
   "en": "\"Congratulations! You're exactly right! ",
   "zh": "「恭喜！汝完全猜對了！",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1536,
   "len": 29,
   "en": "I won't tell you the clue...\"",
   "zh": "俺不會告訴你線索的……」",
   "zh_bytes": 24,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1568,
   "len": 59,
   "en": "\"But I will give you this @hint that may lead you to it...\"",
   "zh": "「不過俺給汝這個@hint（提示），或許能引汝尋著……」",
   "zh_bytes": 43,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1630,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"Search the @chest in @Nystul's room.\"",
   "zh": "「翻翻@chest（寶箱）托房裡那只@Nystul（寶箱）。」",
   "zh_bytes": 30,
   "note": "quest hint!"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1673,
   "len": 77,
   "en": "\"Have you heard the one about the nun, the dragon, and the drunken penguin?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝可聽過那則笑話？關於修女、龍、和醉企鵝的？」",
   "zh_bytes": 48,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1751,
   "len": 2,
   "en": "yn",
   "zh": "yn",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "y/n prompt"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1756,
   "len": 35,
   "en": "\"That's too bad... Neither have I!\"",
   "zh": "「真可惜……俺也沒聽過呢！」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1794,
   "len": 46,
   "en": "\"Good! Maybe you can @teach it to me someday!\"",
   "zh": "「太好啦！說不定哪天你能@teach（教俺）！」",
   "zh_bytes": 33,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1846,
   "len": 67,
   "en": "\"I did my best, did I amuse you? If not, I hope I did confuse you.\"",
   "zh": "「在下盡力了，可博汝一笑？若沒逗笑，也願讓汝糊塗一遭！」",
   "zh_bytes": 56,
   "note": "謝幕語用『在下』"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1916,
   "len": 26,
   "en": "\"Did you enjoy my jokes?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝喜歡俺的笑話嗎？」",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1943,
   "len": 2,
   "en": "yn",
   "zh": "yn",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "y/n prompt"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1955,
   "len": 45,
   "en": "\"Really? I'll just have to try harder, then!\"",
   "zh": "「真的？那俺只好再加把勁啦！」",
   "zh_bytes": 30,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2003,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Why is Dupre like a horseshoe?\"",
   "zh": "「杜普雷為何像個馬蹄鐵？」",
   "zh_bytes": 26,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2038,
   "len": 43,
   "en": "\"It's because they both have the letter 'r'",
   "zh": "「因為兩者裡頭都有字母『r』——西洋話啊",
   "zh_bytes": 39,
   "note": "字母 r 雙關 [r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2082,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "in them!\"",
   "zh": "！」",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "[r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2097,
   "len": 42,
   "en": "\"You did? Then I'll tell you another one!\"",
   "zh": "「喜歡？那俺再說一個給你聽！」",
   "zh_bytes": 30,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2142,
   "len": 65,
   "en": "\"Riddle me this: Do you know what the goose said to the avatar?\" ",
   "zh": "「猜這個謎：汝可知鵝對聖者說了啥？」",
   "zh_bytes": 36,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2208,
   "len": 2,
   "en": "yn",
   "zh": "yn",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "y/n prompt"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2213,
   "len": 91,
   "en": "\"No, no, no, that's not how it works! You're supposed to say you don't, so I can tell you!\"",
   "zh": "「不不不，這樣不對！你該說不知道，俺才好告訴你嘛！」",
   "zh_bytes": 52,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2307,
   "len": 21,
   "en": "\"Let's try it again.\"",
   "zh": "「咱們再試一遍。」",
   "zh_bytes": 18,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2337,
   "len": 22,
   "en": "\"It said 'ankh ankh!'\"",
   "zh": "「牠說『鵝是聖者！』」",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": "honk/ankh 雙關失效 [r2]"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2362,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"What did you think of that one?\"",
   "zh": "「汝覺得這個如何？」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2398,
   "len": 30,
   "en": "\"Well, who asked you, anyway?\"",
   "zh": "「哼，誰問你來著？」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2431,
   "len": 26,
   "en": "\"Oh, that's right, I did!\"",
   "zh": "「噢，對啦，是俺問的！」",
   "zh_bytes": 24,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2460,
   "len": 98,
   "en": "\"Hee hee, ho ho, to spread good cheer I go! Come talk to me again and I'll give you another show!\"",
   "zh": "「嘻嘻哈哈呵呵呵，散播歡樂俺來囉！再來找俺聊一聊，下次給你看新把戲跳！」",
   "zh_bytes": 72,
   "note": "結尾呼應開場 [r2]"
  }
 ],
